Tech2Peace Invites Palestinians and Israelis to join a 12-day
seminar for technology studies in various subjects.
Our program includes:
Python, Graphic Design, AI, Video Editing, and more.
all at a subsidized cost.
The program will be conducted in English,
and we welcome anyone interested in technology and
entrepreneurship between the ages of 20-30
to apply for our program
Apply Now
Tech2Peace provides one-of-a-kind
seminars for young Israeli and
Palestinian adults who participate
in workshops and training sessions
in the fields of technology and
entrepreneurship, along with
dialogue sessions and
extracurricular activities.
Our mission is to bring Jewish and
Arabs between the ages of 20-30
together through mutual high-tech
studies, dialogue, and
entrepreneurship. We strive to build a
young and professional community
that values coexistence,
communication, and professional
collaboration.
Tech2Peace is cultivating a new
reality: Palestinians and Jews
innovating together, leveraging the
power of the high-tech ecosystem
to create a better future for all
people living in the region.
